In the diagram, $R$ is on $QS$ and $QR=8$. Also, $PR=12$, $\angle PRQ=120^\circ$, and $\angle RPS = 90^\circ$. What is the area of $\triangle QPS$? [asy]
//C19
size(10cm); // ADJUST
import olympiad;

// Point coordinates
pair r = (0, 0);
pair q = (-8, 0);
pair p = 12 * dir(60);
pair s = (24, 0);

// draw lines
draw(p--s--r--p--q--r);

// labels
