In the diagram, $K$, $O$ and $M$ are the centers of the three semi-circles. Also, $OC = 32$ and $CB = 36$.

[asy]
pair A, K, O, C, M, B, X, Y, Z, J, T;
O=(0,0);
C=(32,0);
M=(50,0);
B=(68,0);
A=(-68,0);
K=(A+C)/2;
X=(0,68);
Y=(-18,50);
Z=(50,18);
J=(7,43.3);
T=(59,15.6);
path nom, bigc, middlec, smallc;
nom=A--B--(100,100)--(-100,100)--cycle;
bigc=A..X..B--cycle;
middlec=A..Y..C--cycle;
smallc=C..Z..B--cycle;
fill(bigc, gray(.5));
fill(middlec, white);
fill(smallc, white);
draw(smallc);
draw(middlec);
draw(bigc);
